class.description:
This is a basic RSA implementation for GDScript. You generate keys, encrypted, and decrypt with it. [codeblocks] [gdscript] var rsa_module = module_RSA.new(); # Initialize the RSA module. rsa_module.generate_keys(2048); # Generate a key. var plaintext = "Hello, Redot.";
var ciphertext = rsa_module.encrypt(plaintext); # Encrypts, returns String. print("encrypted: ", ciphertext);
var decrypted_text = rsa_module.decrypt(ciphertext); # Decrypts, returns String. print("decrypted: ", decrypted_text); [/gdscript] [/codeblocks]
